title: 110 Realistic 2D Food Icons Fruits and Vegetables for Games
description: Breathe life and detail into your gaming projects with 110 high-quality 2D food icons in artistic realism.
longDescription:
Breathe life and detail into your gaming projects with 110 high-quality 2D food icons in artistic realism. This pack includes a diverse selection of fruits and vegetables, perfect for any game genre that requires detailed, realistic food assets. Whether you’re creating a cooking game, an RPG with a detailed inventory system, or a casual mobile game, these icons will add a professional touch to your project.


Key Features:

110 unique 2D fruit and vegetable icons, carefully crafted in an artistic realism style.

High resolution (512x512 pixels) ensures that your icons will look crisp and detailed, even when scaled.

Transparent PNG files, allowing you to easily integrate the icons into any game or project without having to remove the background.

Versatile use across genres: RPGs, strategy games, mobile games, educational apps and more.

The icons can be used for inventory systems, cooking mechanics, UI elements and in-game items.

Easy Integration:

All icons are ready to use out of the box, with a transparent background for seamless integration into any project.

The uniform 512x512 pixel format allows you to easily resize or customize them to suit your specific needs without losing quality.

The files are provided in PNG format, which is compatible with all major game engines and design tools.

Perfect for Game Developers:

This resource is perfect for developers who need high-quality, realistic food icons but don’t have the time or resources to create them from scratch. Whether you’re creating a medieval RPG or a modern cooking app, this collection offers a wide variety of fruits and vegetables to suit your design.


What you get:

110 unique food icons: the perfect mix of fruits and vegetables in different shapes, sizes and colors.

A clear and consistent style that provides a cohesive look to your game's visual design.

Instant download and easy-to-use files.

Ongoing support and updates:

Version 1 is the first release of the pack, and we are committed to providing ongoing support. If you encounter any issues or need assistance, feel free to contact us!

We encourage you to leave feedback and reviews to help us improve and expand the pack in future updates.

Contact Support: If you have any questions, concerns, or need help with integration, feel free to contact us at olgabutymova27@gmail.com.


We hope these icons will bring creativity and realism to your projects! Don't forget to leave a rating and review!
